  "text": "In this paper, we give a new definition of the generalized inverse with prescribed idempotents and discuss the existences of various different generalized inverses with prescribed idempotents in a Banach algebra. We also give some new characterizations and explicit representations for these generalized inverses. Also, we corrected Theorem 1.4 from [CITATION_1] .",
