    "15404005": {
      "title": "On the (p, q)-outer generalized inverse in Banach algebras",
      "abstract": "Abstract In this note, the ( p , q ) outer generalized inverse in Banach algebra is considered, a new representation based on the (1, 5) inverse is presented. Also, we construct an iterative method for computing the ( p , q ) outer generalized inverse in Banach algebra."
